hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: How do you know each other? docetaxel 100 mg m2 Somebody sent me a bonkers link to the young German woman who was running 100 metres along a race-track in a blue cocktail frock and high sequinned heels. She did it in 14 point-something seconds (I missed the precise time, but I couldn’t bear to re-run the link through the Nurofen ad). I immediately thought of how wrong Andy Warhol was to assume that 15 minutes would be what fame-seekers of the future would get. Seconds, Andy. Fifteen seconds is enough to go round the world 700 million times. Though I instantly forgot her name, I’m sure they’ll remember it in Germany if she comes up as a quiz question.
